E. Acquisition Strategy
The approved DCO-S acquisition strategy is committed to using a modular contracting strategy for fast, agile, and adaptable approaches to successfully develop and
deploy DCO-S. Efforts implement a combined DEVSECOPS framework which incorporates methodologies, technologies, and tools to deeply embed security best
practices into the modern development workflow and tool-chain. USSF plans to leverage new DCO-S prototyping techniques, previous Government investments in
FFRDC efforts, Industry best practices and capability offerings, and Government labs as part of the DCO-S development activities.




