Description: This program delivers a robust and responsive Space Domain Awareness (SDA) and Battle
Management Command and Control (BMC2) capability to meet emerging threats. The program will deliver
capability for decision makers trying to prevent a conflict from extending to space or winning it if it does.
Capabilities and associated infrastructure include, but are not limited to, the following: SDA processing and
exploitation, Indications & Warning (I&W), Planning & Tasking, Theater & Coalition Support, Transmit/Receive,
Dynamic even processing in support of Space Control, Tactical Operations, Commercial Data Integration
and Common Data Management Layer, Platforms and Infrastructure; and Cyber and Threat Warning. The
program maintains foundational Development, Security, and Operations (DevSecOps) enablers such as, but not

                                                                                /Planning/Tasking SW

