security levels), along with modernization of current systems and development of new tools such as test,
training, and exercise software; launch scenario builder; and maneuver processing. Integration of commercial,
contractor, and government applications through incremental software releases.

Improved Data Exchange and Messaging: Establishing machine-to-machine interfaces for common Space
Domain Awareness (SDA) events (conjunction assessment, rendezvous operations, threat processing),
improving integrated messaging and sensor support/tasking/orchestration, and developing a message standard
compliant open architecture to support SDA mission.

Enhanced Situational Awareness and Resiliency: Implementing system resiliency measures and situational
awareness tools to operate in a contested space domain, including integration of commercial capabilities and
