FY 2026 to FY 2027 Increase/Decrease Statement:
The increase of +$0.163 million from FY 2026 and FY 2027 supports expanded research, pilot deployments, and development of
AI/ML-enabled automation capabilities. These investments will accelerate real-time automation adoption, support enterprise-wide
technical assessments, and drive improved efficiency and effectiveness in cyberspace operations.
