D. Acquisition Strategy
The CVN 78 Class of aircraft carriers is designed to replace USS ENTERPRISE and the ships of the NIMITZ Class. The CVN 78 Class features a new nuclear
propulsion and electrical generation/distribution system, Electro Magnetic Aircraft Launch System (EMALS), Advanced Arresting Gear (AAG) system, all electric


