objectives. Once the unit has transitioned to the combined mounted/dismounted fight, the XM30s support the dismounted element with advanced sensors, lethality,
protection, and integrated mission command. This synergy is crucial to the Armored Brigade Combat Team's (ABCT) ability to defeat a near peer competitor.

The XM30 provides a multitude of capabilities; principal among them are enhanced occupant survivability, overmatch lethality, and a modern system architecture with
