B. Accomplishments/Planned Programs ($ in Millions)                                                                                  FY 2024     FY 2025     FY 2026
Security/Operations (DevSecOps) software and Digital Twin technology development approach. DE costs include the software
(SE) licenses for the requirement Product Lifecycle Management (PLM) software, Models Based Systems Engineering (MBSE)
